  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients candidate for elective major (expected duration &gt; 2 hrs) abdominal, urologic,
             and gynecologic surgery

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of diabetes mellitus,

          -  baseline plasma glucose level &gt; 125 mg/dl,

          -  pancreatic resection,

          -  ASA score &gt; 3,

          -  malnutrition (loss of weight greater than 10%),

          -  emergency surgery,

          -  documented gastro-esophageal reflux,

          -  corticosteroid therapy,

          -  ongoing infection,

          -  pregnancy,

          -  age &lt; 18 years,

          -  denied written informed consent
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
